wheere can i see other ads that are currently running? I wantto learn how best to create an advertisement from existing ones running on newsbreak

To see other ads currently running on NewsBreak, you can explore the types of ad formats and placements available. This will give you an idea of how ads are positioned and optimized for performance. Unfortunately, there isn't a direct way to view all active ads, but understanding the ad formats can help you create effective advertisements. You can check out this guide for more information: [Types of NewsBreak Ad Formats and Placements](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20229876903053-Types-of-NewsBreak-Ad-Formats-and-Placements). Let me know if you need further assistance!
ok so there is no library where i can see existing running ads?

That's correct, there isn't a library or feature on NewsBreak where you can view all existing running ads. However, you can use the ad creation tools to preview different ad formats and placements, which can give you insights into how ads are typically displayed. If you have any other questions or need help with creating your ad, feel free to ask!
